name: testPreviewDescriptionFromEditInformationPage
description: Verification of presence preview description of build from Edit Information Page for Freestyle Project
descriptionHtml: Verification of presence preview description of build from Edit Information Page for Freestyle Project

testStage.description: Verification of presence preview description of build from Edit Information Page for Freestyle Project

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click Edit Buld Information on the side bar menu
Input the description 'DESCRIPTION_TEXTy1PR1RS in the 'Description' field on the Edit Build Information page
Click on the 'Preview' button on the Edit Build Information page
Get Preview text on the Edit Build Information page
Logout from instance http://localhost:8081/
